node.text: Our very first IG Live session with @alexchacon_official, a filmmaker and YouTuber from Texas, USA with over 355k thousand followers. We talk about Alex’s inspiring journey, from quitting medical school, selling everything he owned, and driving his motorcycle from Alaska to Argentina in 500 days. He’s traveled to over 70 countries while working on several projects with renowned brands and tourism boards all around the world. We ask Alex about his craziest travel experiences, how he grew and monetizes his following, and more! #TheGlobeWanderer #DigitalMarketerElite #digitalnomad

node.text: On today’s IG Live session, we are very excited to be interviewing @alexchacon_official, a filmmaker and YouTuber from Texas, USA with over 355k thousand followers. Alex’s journey began when he quit medical school, sold everything he had and drove his motorcycle from Alaska to Argentina in 500 days. Since then he’s traveled to over 70 countries while working on several projects with renowned brands and tourism boards all around the world. We’ll talk more about Alex’s incredible story, his craziest travel experiences, how he grew and monetizes his following, and more on our IG Live later at 9PM (+8 GMT) or 7AM EST, July 30th. See you all there! #TheGlobeWanderer #DigitalMarketerElite #digitalnomad
